Saturday and Sunday race tickets located in Grandstand C, just before turn one and adjacent to our hospitality suite 
Driver autographs and "meet and greet" sessions for Enron customers and executives 
Opportunity to network with companies including (but not limited to): NEXTEL, JP Morgan Chase, Gemstar, Pennzoil, PPG, Snap-On, Bosch, Freightliner, Toyota, Panasonic, 3D Village 


This package is available for the weekend on a per day basis.  Enron has available 100 passes per day, and pricing is as follows:

Saturday Only                   $150 per person 
Sunday Only                     $250 per person 


Please see the following attachments, as they will provide you the first look at the Enron/PacWest Racing car and the schedule of events.  Please contact David Tagliarino (853-7883) or Greg Grissom (345-8741) by Friday, September 28 to secure your package for this exciting weekend.   

